OL,3,CFundraiser for Liverpool fan with
OL,4,Ccerebral palsy hopes to 'give Ryan a
OL,5,Cvoice'
OL,7,FThe family of a lifelong Liverpool fan
OL,8,Fwith cerebral palsy are hoping to
OL,9,Fraise the funds for a life changing
OL,10,Fpiece of technology that will allow
OL,11,Fhim to communicate like never before.
OL,13,FRyan Edwards, from Wallasey, has
OL,14,Frequired round the clock care and a
OL,15,Fbreathing machine his entire life, but
OL,16,Fhis family say that's never stopped
OL,17,Fthe "bright and funny" 32-year-old
OL,18,Ffrom being the happy person he is.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
