OL,3,CFundraiser for Liverpool fan with
OL,4,Ccerebral palsy hopes to 'give Ryan a
OL,5,Cvoice'
OL,7,FHis younger sister, Samantha Edwards,
OL,8,Fsaid: "He's got the most gorgeous
OL,9,Fsmile. People say they wish they could
OL,10,Fjust bottle up his laugh and it could
OL,11,Fbe given out to everyone. He's got
OL,12,Fsuch an aura about him that everyone
OL,13,Fdeserves to see."
OL,15,FRyan is non-verbal and his family rely
OL,16,Fon visual cues to understand what he
OL,17,Fneeds, but that all changed when he
OL,18,Ftook part in a trial for a
OL,19,Fcommunication device that allowed him
OL,20,Fto control a computer with his eyes
OL,21,Fand have it speak aloud for him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
