OL,3,CFundraiser for Liverpool fan with
OL,4,Ccerebral palsy hopes to 'give Ryan a
OL,5,Cvoice'
OL,7,FSamantha said: "In that time it was
OL,8,Ffantastic. He was able to tell us he
OL,9,Floves us, he was able to tell us what
OL,10,Fhe wanted to do, even things like
OL,11,Fwatch TV. We were absolutely amazed."
OL,13,FBut after the three week trial, Ryan's
OL,14,Ffamily were told he doesn't meet the
OL,15,Fcriteria for funding to keep the
OL,16,Fequipment permanently.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
