OL,3,CFundraiser for Liverpool fan with
OL,4,Ccerebral palsy hopes to 'give Ryan a
OL,5,Cvoice'
OL,7,FSamantha said: "It's really
OL,8,Ffrustrating... but we woke up one day
OL,9,Fand just thought you know what? We're
OL,10,Fgoing to get it. We're going to fight
OL,11,Ffor it."
OL,13,FRyan's family have now set up a
OL,14,Ffundraiser to secure the #12,000 they
OL,15,Fneed to pay for a permanent Smartbox
OL,16,Feye gaze communication device.
OL,18,FSamantha has dedicated herself to
OL,19,Fhelping Ryan as a member of his 24
OL,20,Fhour care team, and says the device
OL,21,Fwould change everything.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
