OL,5,Cvoice'
OL,7,FSamantha said: "It will open his world
OL,8,Fcompletely. Just being able to
OL,9,Fcommunicate as any 32 year old adult
OL,10,Fwould. He's got so much in his brain
OL,11,Fthat needs to get out, but he can't
OL,12,Fwithout this technology.
OL,14,F"There's such an opportunity to
OL,15,Fexpress his thoughts. Being able to
OL,16,Fknow the littlest things will change
OL,17,Feverything for him."
